AGREEMENT ON THE EUROPEAN  ECONOMIC AREA  (OJ No L 1, 3.1.1994, p. 3; and EFTA States’ official gazettes) Amended by: 
1. Protocol Adjusting the Agreement on the European Economic Area of 17 March 1993 (OJ No L 1, 3.1.1994, p. 572; and EFTA States’ official gazettes). 


2. EEA Council Decision No 1/95 of 10 March on the entry into force of the Agreement on the European Economic Area for the Principality of Liechtenstein (OJ No L 86, 20.4.1995, p. 58; EEA Supplement No 14, 20.4.1995, p. 1). 


